  "prompt": "Which are the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi?",
  "response": "Delhi has several reputable IELTS coaching institutes that can help students prepare for the exam. Here are some of the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi:\n\n1. **British Council**: They offer structured IELTS preparation courses with experienced instructors and official materials.\n\n2. **IDP Education**: IDP, one of the co-owners of the IELTS exam, provides training that aligns closely with the test format.\n\n3. **Manya Group (The Princeton Review)**: Known for its comprehensive coaching and regular mock tests, Manya Group has a good track record for IELTS preparation.\n\n4. **EnglishEdge**: This institute focuses on enhancing language skills with a curriculum designed for international exams, including IELTS.\n\n5. **Gateway Abroad**: They offer personalized coaching sessions and intensive courses for IELTS aspirants.\n\n6. **Career Launcher**: Known for its coaching in competitive examinations, it also provides effective IELTS training programs.\n\n7. **A homogeneous group of English Language Institute (AGE) Institute**: They provide specific language training tailored for test-takers.\n\n8. **Koto**: They focus on communication skills and IELTS preparation with a practical approach.\n\n9. **Vidyasaarathi**: Offers customized coaching and workshops aimed at improving IELTS scores.\n\n10. **intellipath**: Known for its online and offline IELTS preparation courses, they offer flexible learning options.\n\nWhen choosing an institute, consider factors like the teaching methodology, batch size, faculty experience, course materials, and student reviews. Additionally, visiting the institutes for a trial class can help make a more informed decision.",
